sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor Admin as OrgOwnerAdmin
participant Client as WebClient
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant OrgAuth as OrgProtectAuthorize
participant DeptCtrl as DepartmentController
participant ChannelCtrl as ChannelControllerAlias
participant OrgDb as MongoDepartmentChannelMembership
participant ChatSvc as ChatService
Admin->>Client: Tao department
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/organizations/:orgId/departments
Gateway->>OrgAuth: protect + authorize owner/admin
OrgAuth-->>Gateway: pass
Gateway->>DeptCtrl: createDepartment
DeptCtrl->>OrgDb: insert Department
DeptCtrl-->>Client: 201
Admin->>Client: Tao channel trong department
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/organizations/:orgId/departments/:deptId/channels
Gateway->>ChannelCtrl: createChannel
ChannelCtrl->>OrgDb: insert Channel
ChannelCtrl-->>Client: 201
Admin->>Client: Xoa channel
Client->>Gateway: DELETE /api/.../channels/:id
Gateway->>ChannelCtrl: deleteChannel
ChannelCtrl->>OrgDb: set isActive=false
ChannelCtrl-->>Client: 200
ChatSvc->>Gateway: GET /api/organizations/:orgId/accessible-channel-ids
Gateway->>DeptCtrl: getAccessibleChannelIds
DeptCtrl->>OrgDb: compute by membership + channel members
